    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Acrobatics beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.LQw0yIMDUJJkq1nD]{Cat Fall}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.bJ4tF95Byy7wCS65]{Rolling Landing}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.1CgxvFwVXKDSgcVr]{Poise Path - Trained}</strong>: Even in difficult situations your movement remains robust, deliberate and controlled.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.M2a2oBkildqF5EWO]{Flow Path - Trained}</strong>: Your movements flow into one another, making you agile and hard to catch.</li></ul>",
